        "created_at": "2024-07-26T05:25:04.871Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Now SIGNAL supports message scheduling. Another messenger Telegram, after sending a scheduled message, creates an Android notification and marks this chat as unread. This makes monitoring the schedule more convenient, for example it will remind to check the delivery status and read status of a sent message. I would suggest implementing this functionality in SIGNAL as well.</p>",
