        "created_at": "2024-07-26T17:56:19.491Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I see. I just did some more testing on my Android, because it worked for me earlier (I tested it before posting). But it didn’t work for me either now so I did some more testing and I learned that it only works if you have Signal Desktop open as well. So maybe the workaround is not helpful for you.</p>\n<p>I’m not sure whether this is a bug or not so I will send my test results to Signal so they can decide what the expected behavior should be and fix if it’s a bug.</p>\n<p>Anyway, it was just a tip as a possible workaround. Hopefully somebody from Signal finds your feature request</p>",
